{"type": "article", "id": 10077, "title": "日本设计师用蓝天大海设计了一个幼儿园", "description": "选址的确独一无二，但设计师基于自然环境的改造也值得一看。", "date": "2015-05-28T10:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 10722, "name": "日本长崎"}, {"id": 4187, "name": "幼儿园"}], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 323, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144213RIU3jbM9pcxDzJde.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t近日<a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/635225/ob-kindergarten-and-nursery-hibinosekkei-youji-no-shiro/\" target=\"_blank\"> archdaily 网站</a>贴出了一组日本长崎县幼儿园的照片，这个幼儿园是由设计事务所 <a href=\"http://hibinosekkei.com/top.html\">HIBINOSEKKEI</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.e-ensha.com/\">Youji no Shiro</a> 共同设计的，它依山傍海，完全处于自然环境中。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144206KcgjL8i2SlvxPuOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t如果孩子们在屋顶的平台上玩耍，可以吹到近在咫尺的海风。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144206oPLh9DTnfeM6r4Eu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t上图是幼儿园餐厅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144207gD6zP51o7bOaICAX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t幼儿园餐厅，高高的顶棚和大玻璃窗，视野宽阔。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144208GYChXm3Zu84v05fc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t排队打饭的地方。木质的地板，孩子们在餐厅也光脚行走。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144208rmfJh5yb4Tkec81g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t另一个角度的餐厅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214420920XUqF7grvlpyM6L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t活动空间，一些开放的课程可以在这里进行，比如绘画课。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144209kvopeMs2fP6Alw7q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t从另一个角度看餐厅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144210VKZUBg4E7eQsul9N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t活动教室。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144210uSYCfGEktQBbx703.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t活动和休闲空间。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144211I5Wk4HiQGUNLRbnJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t阅读空间。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144211KIe3JXQ1wWBau4Ag.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t幼儿园还设有许多矮台阶可以攀爬，按照设计师的话来说，这种设计是为了“增强孩子们的触感，改变心情。”\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144212HfkQEWpZ6BFTljP2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t如果愿意，孩子们可以一直爬到屋顶去，远处就是大海。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t其实设计师事务所 hibinosekkei 设计过不少出色的作品。他们曾获得过 2011 年 Good Design Award 和 2014 年的 Kids Design Award ，下图是他们<a href=\"http://hibino-fukushi.com\" target=\"_blank\">设计过的养老院</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144212Gz48FEvWRe2Zap69.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/635225/ob-kindergarten-and-nursery-hibinosekkei-youji-no-shiro/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><em>archdaily</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}